":469733,"uid":93784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:35:15.000Z","msg":"改到個立法會變左畸型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直頭係控制左個議會"},{"pid":"726e1580ba0d44da1d9fb0aafcba9aad0493f118","tid":469733,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:45:01.000Z","msg":"dq+剪布+釋法<br />\n玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30059f9a677db7be31831f27241637664c0f263","tid":469733,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T21:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第七十五條 <br />\n香港特別行政區立法會舉行會議的法定人數為不少於全體議員的二分之一。 <br />\n立法會議事規則由立法會自行制定，但不得與本法相抵觸。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n釋法釋到70*1/2=20？<br />\n你班柒頭坐定定啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明支共派過35人，只要你班柒頭坐定定咪點唔到人數囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府：二分一即係幾多人係我話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話20就20啦</blockquote><br />\n但中共未必咁諗<br />\n中共：咁多錢蛇齋餅傻推你班柒頭上位，連坐定定都唔想，要煩鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實建制派係想改「全體委員會」法定人數，唔係大會法定人數。如果釋法可以話第七十五條只限制大會法定人數唔包括「全體委員會」。"},{"pid":"1e4b1523d86cfaa77bbe708739808af018faa4d1","tid":469733,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcd6f6280af80bbec4c0ad8c9734e54dd9dfcf2","tid":469733,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike"